      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. It will require major mechanical overhaul, as the engine suffers from a cracked head gasket and the transmission frequently slips out of gear. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it will need to be towed from its current location.",
