    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the pristine interior appointments to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a rigorous standard of maintenance synonymous with investment-grade assets. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically peerless, this offering provides a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a definitive example of the marque.",
